         <abstract id="aspace_2b4f9c21b8c487dbbd1e6f72d173c3d4">Correspondence, diaries, and sermons document Saxton's evangelistic work. Noah C. Saxton (1798-ca. 1834) was an evangelist in Connecticut, New Jersey, and New York.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part>Saxton, Noah C.</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
